# MBRACE INSIGHT - CLIENT DASHBOARD UPDATE
## Redesigned for Mission-Driven Positioning & Clear ROI Communication

---

## DASHBOARD ARCHITECTURE

The dashboard now serves three audiences simultaneously:

1. **The Contractor (You)** - Shows your blind spots, missing revenue, optimization opportunities
2. **The Homeowner** (if they see it) - Shows professional systems, response times, local expertise
3. **The Investor/Decision Maker** - Shows ROI, month-over-month improvements, market dominance metrics

---

