7. Settings (integrations, preferences)

**Sidebar (Always Visible):**
- Current month KPIs
- Quick actions
- Recent alerts
- Schedule strategy call

**Footer:**
- "Questions? Schedule a call" link
- Documentation/help links
- Contact support

