## KEY METRICS DEFINITIONS

**Close Rate**
Estimates converted to paying customers
Formula: Closed jobs Ã· Estimates given Ã— 100
Industry average: 24%
Your goal: 40%+

**Customer Acquisition Cost (CAC)**
Total cost to acquire one paying customer
Formula: (Marketing spend + Estimate labor cost) Ã· Closed jobs
Industry average: $1,400
Your target: < $1,000

**Lifetime Value (LTV)**
Total revenue expected from average customer
Calculation: Initial job + maintenance revenue + referral revenue
Your average: $29,700

**ROI**
Return on marketing investment
Formula: (Revenue - Spend) Ã· Spend Ã— 100
Industry average: 320%
Your target: 800%+

**After-Hours Capture**
Percentage of after-hours calls successfully captured
Formula: After-hours calls answered Ã· Total after-hours calls Ã— 100
Your goal: 80%+

**Response Time**
Average time from call to first human response
Your target: < 10 minutes
Your actual: 8 minutes

