## INTEGRATION POINTS

Dashboard pulls data from:
- Google Local Services Ads (automated daily)
- Google Ads (Facebook, YouTube if applicable)
- Call tracking system (CallRail or equivalent)
- CRM (estimates, conversions, customer data)
- Accounting software (revenue attribution)
- AI answering system (call analytics)

Updates: Real-time for calls, daily for spend/revenue, weekly for summaries

